; A. Description
;    A list of commands here configures SCU LVD and generates Low Voltage reset.
;
; B. Preparation
;    Supply power to external power port by a suitable instrument or make a environment to generate low voltage.
;
; C. Prerequisite Example (abov_example_config.h)
;    1. SCULVD
;    2. COA
;
; For more information, read a user's manual of the target device carefully.
;
; SCULVD
; 1. LVR                       : [ e 0 ]
;    Interrupt Enable          : e (Maskable Interrupt)
;    Detect Level              : 0 (This feature is not available.)
;
;
; COA
sendln 'cm coa'
mpause 30
sendln 'lvrcfg -rst l -volt 6'
mpause 30
sendln 'writecfg'
mpause 100

; SCU
sendln 'cm scu'
mpause 30
sendln 'reset'
pause 2

; SCULVD
sendln 'cm sculvd'
mpause 30
sendln 'lvr e 0'
